{"tid":58010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駐日代表處是否更名 台灣外交部：審慎評估","createTime":"2016-12-28T13:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T09:04:11.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0999157f78f44b6e5bd8144b9bea8bb120ae6d83","tid":58010,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"駐日代表處是否更名　外交部：審慎評估<br />\n<br />\n日本駐台機構明年起將更名為「日本台灣交流協會」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">外界關注我對日交涉機構亞東關係協會與台北駐日經濟文化代表處是否也要更名？</span></span>外交部晚間表示，外交部將秉持強化台日交流、明確反映我對日工作機構內涵及參酌國內民意等原則審慎評估。<br />\n<br />\n對於我涉日事務單位是否更名，總統府說，涉及與駐在國默契與約定，相關單位會尋求與駐在國的共識審慎考量。<br />\n（陳培煌、陳郁仁/台北報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161228/1022884/papersec_right\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161228%2F1022884%2Fpapersec_right&d=vxBuxWVO3%2B2ha190jfl7IksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=e40cbd2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161228/1022884/papersec_right</a>"},{"pid":"539f3de6a1cbfa5694d06f6b50e169078d676e0e","tid":58010,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b751a5d9f1db1427cc9ef5a1bca83d132765bd49","tid":58010,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"唔好比我估中<br />\n民進黨政府髮夾彎<br />\n小英變成女版馬英9"},{"pid":"08241761ce8535a238fc77d01895b71c60bd4127","tid":58010,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好比我估中<br />\n民進黨政府髮夾彎<br />\n小英變成女版馬英9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n民進黨根本唔係台獨黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舐台撚仲井底過台狗"},{"pid":"1571ca1c10f68ac045ae4ca1b4df07426fffcfa0","tid":58010,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28